data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful move-in ready home! With 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a newly renovated master bathroom, this property offers both style and functionality.
The kitchen features 42'' espresso cabinets, quartz countertops, and all stainless steel appliances, including a washer and dryer. . Throughout the house, you'll find plank
-style ceramic tile flooring, with plush carpeting in the bedrooms. The screened-in lanai, above-ground pool, and cute yard space provide ample outdoor living opportunity,
